      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously curated example of precision engineering. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full Vanos overhaul and reinforced subframe mounting points to ensure absolute structural rigidity under load. The high-revving power plant exhibits razor-sharp throttle response with a perfectly linear power delivery. Featuring strategic OEM+ enhancements, the suspension geometry has been optimized for surgical turn-in precision and high-speed stability. The finish retains incredible depth, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who values mechanical integrity and peak performance.",
