      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in S54 engineering, preserved in showroom condition. We\u2019ve addressed the common failure points with surgical precision: full subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Besian Systems VANOS overhaul. The compression across all six cylinders remains within factory tolerances, delivering the razor-sharp throttle response and linear power delivery this high-revving straight-six is legendary for. The chassis is exceptionally tight, featuring a dialed-in suspension geometry optimized for neutral turn-in and zero bushing deflection. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen that performs with the mechanical harmony of a factory-fresh machine. Truly a 'no-stories' vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak performance.",
